        <summary>Gets the captured substring from the input string.</summary>
        <value>The substring that is captured by the match.</value>
        <remarks>
            If a call to the <see cref="M:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex.Match(System.String)" /> or <see cref="M:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Match.NextMatch" /> method fails to
            find a match, the value of the returned <c>Match.Value</c> property is <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.
            If the regular expression engine is unable to match a capturing group, the value of the returned
            <c>Group.Value</c> property is <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.
